<h1><%= title %></h1>
<p>Welcome to <strong>LocalLibrary</strong>, a very basic Express website developed as a tutorial example on the Mozilla Developer Network.</p>
<h2>Dynamic content</h2>
<p>The library has the following record counts:</p>
<ul>
  <li>
    <strong>Movies:</strong> <%= movie_count %>
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>Copies:</strong> <%= movie_instance_count %>
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>Copies available:</strong> <%= movie_instance_available_count %>
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>Directors:</strong> <%= director_count %>
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>Genres:</strong> <%= genre_count %>
  </li>
</ul>